# ── Evaluation Procedure is a Core Concept ──
# "No Evaluation" is the explicit opt-out — keep it readable so users
# don't read the dropdown's "None" entry as a missing-data bug.

Pairwise Comparison is an Evaluation Procedure
Automated (Hold-out) is an Evaluation Procedure
K-fold Cross-validation is an Evaluation Procedure
No Evaluation is an Evaluation Procedure

# ── Link procedures to their interface templates ──
# The interface defines the DAG shape; the procedure name is the user-facing label.

Automated (Hold-out) implements Holdout Evaluation
K-fold Cross-validation implements KFold Evaluation
